Let $\alpha$, $\beta$ and $\gamma$ be cuts.
Let:
{{begin-eqn}}
{{eqn | n = 1
      | l = \alpha
      | o = <
      | r = \beta
}}
{{eqn | n = 2
      | l = \beta
      | o = <
      | r = \gamma
}}
